Let’s get real.
.
Inequality among minorities happened all over the world.
Of course, Indonesia has health and economic issues in certain regions, most of them due to inequality cases and still occurs frequently. The government has the obligation to strive social and health care solutions, without considering race or religion. We all know that  Indonesia has the perfect ideology, sounding unity in diversity, social justice and equality for the people. So why we don't fight for that?
Support the spirit of equality! If you don't start it with little things from now, then when? Every single people has the right to be equal. What are you doing about #ReducedInequalities ?
.
